title: 10 Takeaways from Week 2
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 2
description:
DJ and Bucky reunite after an amazing weekend of football to give their Week 2 takeaways, including – Patrick Mahomes should have had MORE touchdowns versus the Steelers (1:00), Blake Bortles can get the job done (3:20), Sean McVay is way ahead of the league (17:10) and did the Giants make a mistake not drafting a quarterback early (30:30)?
